desc: Ask Slackbot to send you an export listing all workspace members using unsupported software, presented as a zipped CSV file.

token.desc: Authentication token bearing required scopes. Tokens should be passed as an HTTP Authorization header or alternatively, as a POST parameter.

date_sessions_started.desc: Unix timestamp of a date to start looking for user sessions. If not provided will start six months ago.

date_end_of_support.desc: Unix timestamp of the date of past or upcoming end of support cycles. If not provided will include all announced end of support cycles.

could_not_export.desc: For some reason, the export could not be started

invalid_team_id.desc: The team ID passed is invalid

missing_scope.desc: The calling token is not granted the necessary scopes to complete this operation.
